## Don't do these

- Don't use `here::here()` ‚Äî absolute paths from project root only
- Don't call `get_db_connection()` with arguments ‚Äî reads from `config.yml`
- Don't store credentials anywhere ‚Äî redirect to `config.yml`
- Don't reference SonarQube ‚Äî retired; lizard is the complexity source
- Don't conflate Testray routine 590307 (acceptance) and 82964 (release)
- Don't collapse `FixManagementAnalysis.R` and `FixManagementDashboard.Rmd`
- Don't recalibrate `max_ccn` p95 = 16 silently ‚Äî document in `scoring_normalization`
- Don't remove ticket ID tokens from TF-IDF ‚Äî they are valid signals
- Don't treat `tech_debt_minutes` as a scoring input ‚Äî display only
- Don't filter LDA topic chart by `year` ‚Äî use `period` field
